%F A082840 G.f.: -(1 -6*x +2*x^2)/((1 - x)*(1 - 4*x + x^2)).
%F A082840 a(n) = -3/2 + (1/12)*( (a -2*b +5)*a^n + (b -2*a +5)*b^n ), with a = 2 + sqrt(3), b = 2 - sqrt(3):.
